<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038373" n="142r"/>
<p>
<lb/>Negotia <add>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> sub ingressum novorum studiorum hic mihi pera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genda <del>erant </del>fuerunt, citam ad gratissimas Tuas <rs key="B_991170517038705501 B_991170517038905501" type="letters">Literas</rs> re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sponsionem impediverunt, quod te non moleste laturum
               <lb/>spero. En igitur <rs key="biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblio">libellum</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-100704514" type="person">Wetstenii</rs>, quem cum exigui
               <lb/>pretii sit, si tanquam leve munusculum accipies, gratum
               <lb/>facies. Gaudeo Te invenisse qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam in <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <rs key="B_991170517039105501" type="letter">epistola</rs>
<pb facs="1038374" n="142v"/>
<lb/>ad rem quam tractas pertinentia. Secutus consilium Tuum
               <lb/>scripsi ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>Secr.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1222289342" type="person">Gadaldinum</rs>,<del> cumque rogavi,</del> ut ipsum redi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tus mei certiorem facerem atque rogarem, ut cultum meum
               <lb/>et obsequia deferat ad <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930 pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175" type="persons">Reformatores</rs>. Fra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>trem <abbr>Exc.</abbr> Domin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178493288" type="person">Mari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Labia</rs>, quam meo nomine reve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rere, huc regressum crastina die salutabo. Gratias Tibi
               <lb/>ago pro amica invitatione in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des Tuas, libertate ista <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te
               <lb/>mihi donata forte utar, quando Venetias invisam. Salutat
               <lb/>Te <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenus</rs> rogatque ut adjunctum <rs key="biblio_KGKQAP5S biblio_8JCIWHQ6 biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblios">fasciculum</rs>
<lb/>ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1037587715" type="person">Ertz</rs> perferri cures.
            </p>
<closer><salute>Vale et me ama.</salute>
<lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1717-11-10"><choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> 10. 9bris 1717</date>.</dateline>
</closer>
</div>
